11) Evaluation Metrics (make it real)

Track:

* Save rate (memory proxy)
* Rewrites/reposts (pattern adoption)
* Comments referencing feeling (“felt this”, “I see it”)
* Recall after delay (can it be retold?)

⸻

12) Upgrade: “Experience Density”

New metric:

Experience Density = (sensory activation + emotional weight) / word count

Goal:

* maximize felt impact
* minimize length

⸻

